OL,7,FTaxi driver Urfan Sharif, 42, told
OL,8,Fjurors he "took full responsibility"
OL,9,Ffor Sara's death at the Old Bailey on
OL,10,FWednesday, whilst his wife Beinash
OL,11,FBatool, 30, sobbed in the dock.
OL,13,FPreviously, Sharif had sought to blame
OL,14,FBatool for killing his daughter but on
OL,15,FWednesday told jurors: "I accept every
OL,16,Fsingle thing."
